news_header: Strikes affect logistics and store operations in Finland.
news_original_title: Maitohyllyt tyhjenivät, mutta olutta on – tältä näyttää kauppojen hyllyillä nyt eri puolilla Suomea
news_text: A trade strike in Finland began in logistics and will extend to stores, lasting three days. Consumers are advised against hoarding food, and while some products may be temporarily unavailable, overall stock levels remain stable. The CEO of the Federation of Commerce emphasizes that stores will remain open and well-stocked.
